lll_NoTaskW:%0 can't run in a TaskWindow
lll_Arc:%0 does not work on Archimedes or A5000-like systems, to boot Linux on these systems you must use !Linux, which is available from http://www.arm.uk.linux.org/~rmk/armlinux.html
lll_uksys:Sorry, %0 does not support this system
lll_nomem:Out of memory (malloc failed)
lll_toolong:Kernel command line to long (maxinum length 256)
lll_unrec:Unrecognised

